msgid "gluon-config-mode:welcome"
msgstr ""
"<p>Welcome to the setup wizard of your new Freifunk-Trier node.</"
"p><p>Please choose a hostname that follows the pattern &lt;ZIP&gt;-&lt;"
"fantasyname&gt; (e.g. 54290-unicorn), where ZIP refers to the postal code "
"at the location the node is going to be set up at and fantasyname can be "
"freely chosen.</p><p>In case you want to limit the bandwidth used for the "
"mesh vpn, please note that at least 100 kBit/s are necessary, because of "
"the base load (ca. 30kBit/s) each router generates.</p>"

msgid "gluon-config-mode:pubkey"
msgstr ""
"This is the public key of your Freifunk node. Only after it has been "
"deployed on the servers of Freifunk Trier, the router can connect to "
"the mesh-vpn. Therefore please send its name (<em><%=hostname%></em>) and "
"public key (<em><%=pubkey%></em>) to <a href=\"mailto:trier-keys@freifunk.net?"
"subject=Registration:%20<%=hostname%>&amp;body=%23%20<%=hostname%>%0A"
"%23%20<%=sysconfig.primary_mac%>%0Akey%20%22<%=pubkey%>%22%3B"
"\">trier-keys@freifunk.net</a>."

msgid "gluon-config-mode:novpn"
msgstr ""
"<p>You have selected <strong>not</strong> to use the mesh VPN. "
"Your node will only be able to connect to the Freifunk network if other nodes in reach "
"already have a connection.</p>"

msgid "gluon-config-mode:reboot"
msgstr ""
"<p>Your node is currently restarting and afterwards will try to connect to "
"Freifunk nodes nearby. More information regarding your local Freifunk "
"community can be found on <a href=\"https://trier.freifunk.net\">our "
"website</a>.</p><p>Thank you for running a node and have fun exploring the "
"world of Freifunk!</p>"


msgid "gluon-config-mode:altitude-label"
msgstr "Altitude"

msgid "gluon-config-mode:altitude-help"
msgstr ""
"Specifying the altitude is optional and should only be done if a proper "
"value is known."
